ime":"2019-09-01T05:16:27.000Z","msg":"下次真係捉呢d<br />\n搵夠5,6個對1個先好黎料<br />\n佢地一定係飛虎隊果d, 因為預左比人捉到要甩身<br />\n飛虎隊體能要求有幾高大家都知"},{"pid":"77fbd409249a172b84c5dd4a9100c4bb4d22a221","tid":1525832,"uid":268824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:19:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}